(3.5 Protocol Constraint Interpretation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Atho?s parameter regime is built around moderate cadence with deterministic maturity and bounded) Tj
T*
(capacity:) Tj
T*
(- A 120 second cadence reduces extreme orphan-pressure relative to very short block intervals) Tj
T*
(while retaining practical settlement progression.) Tj
T*
(- 6 confirmation policy reflects a balance between user UX and finality confidence under) Tj
T*
(expected reorg distributions.) Tj
T*
(- 150 block coinbase maturity restricts immediate spendability of newly mined outputs, reducing) Tj
T*
(short-cycle manipulation surfaces.) Tj
T*
(- The 1 atom/vB floor and 500 atom absolute minimum fee provide a simple two-layer anti-spam) Tj
T*
(filter.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3.6 Engineering Implication) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Policy constants are not independent knobs. In Atho, a change in fee floor or block cap alters:) Tj
T*
(- mempool admission behavior,) Tj
T*
(- miner packing economics,) Tj
T*
(- miner packing economics,) Tj
T*
(- private transaction cost presentation,) Tj
T*
(- and wallet fee estimator assumptions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
