T*
() Tj
T*
(Transaction verification, block verification, proof-of-work checks, miner-fee closure, and) Tj
T*
(private-state checks execute in deterministic verifier paths. Optional accelerators \(for) Tj
T*
(example, batch UTXO checks\) do not alter acceptance semantics; they alter execution efficiency) Tj
T*
(only.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
