T*
() Tj
T*
(CPU and GPU miners are execution backends on one consensus rule path. Engine choice should not) Tj
T*
(change block validity semantics. This is an important property: performance heterogeneity) Tj
T*
(without consensus heterogeneity.) Tj
T*
() Tj
