T*
() Tj
T*
(The architecture split limits blast radius:) Tj
T*
(- UI/API faults should not directly mutate consensus state.) Tj
T*
(- Native binary faults are bounded by pinning and loading policy checks.) Tj
T*
(- Accounting correctness is centralized in verifier paths, not client UIs.) Tj
T*
(- Miner performance optimizations do not rewrite consensus semantics.) Tj
