T*
(- Domain-separated role address derivation.) Tj
T*
(- Binary pinning digest metadata surfaces.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The 48-byte digest width supports consistent identity surfaces and stronger collision-resistance) Tj
T*
(margin than shorter digest choices for consensus-adjacent identities.[^10]) Tj
T*
() Tj
