T*
() Tj
T*
(Atho separates internal and external address surfaces:) Tj
T*
(- Internal canonical identity: HPK bytes.) Tj
T*
(- User-facing representation: Base56 encoded strings with role/network prefixes and checksum) Tj
T*
(behavior.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This decoupling allows ergonomic display without weakening canonical identity semantics.) Tj
T*
() Tj
