T*
() Tj
T*
(Domain separation is used in multiple critical contexts:) Tj
T*
(- Role address derivation \(ATHO_ADDR_V1, ATHO_BOND_V1, ATHO_STAKE_V1\).) Tj
T*
(- Protocol pool address derivation domains by network.) Tj
T*
(- Private note and nullifier derivation domains.) Tj
T*
(- Signing preimage domains for private spends.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Domain separation reduces replay and cross-context confusion. It should be preserved whenever) Tj
T*
(adding new cryptographic contexts.) Tj
T*
() Tj
