T*
() Tj
T*
(The active schedule is not an era-halving curve. It operates as daily reward decay:) Tj
T*
(- Start with 100.00000 ATHO/block.) Tj
T*
(- Hold that reward constant for one full 720-block day.) Tj
T*
(- Apply the fixed-point multiplier once at the next day boundary.) Tj
T*
(- Carry integer remainder so cumulative issuance reaches the cap exactly.) Tj
T*
(- After the final scheduled positive-subsidy block, subsidy becomes 0.) Tj
T*
