T*
(- Freeze risky administrative mutations.) Tj
T*
(- Capture logs and state snapshots for forensic continuity.) Tj
T*
(- Verify runtime guard and pin integrity status.) Tj
T*
(- Isolate whether incident is local config drift, artifact drift, or consensus-level anomaly.) Tj
